OL,7,FAt their first meeting of the season
OL,8,FPremier League clubs did not spend a
OL,9,Fsingle second talking about Manchester
OL,10,FCity's legal challenge over
OL,11,Frestrictions to sponsorship deals.
OL,13,FThis could be an indication the league
OL,14,Fchampions have lost their
OL,15,Fcontroversial case over Associated
OL,16,FParty Transactions (APT).
