OL,7,FBut of course the lack of discussion
OL,8,Ftoday might also mean a decision
OL,9,Fresulting from the arbitration process
OL,10,Fthey instigated hasn't been handed
OL,11,Fdown, its judgement is yet to be made
OL,12,Fpublic - in short, that process is
OL,13,Fstill ongoing.
OL,15,FBecause of the Premier League's
OL,16,Finsistence on secrecy, few know the
OL,17,Ftruth. Given the significance of what
OL,18,Fis being judged, given its impact on
OL,19,Fthe league and by extension millions
OL,20,Fof football fans, the lack of
OL,21,Ftransparency feels archaic.
