OL,7,FThe current APT rules were brought in
OL,8,Ffollowing the Saudi takeover of
OL,9,FNewcastle United. They were designed
OL,10,Fto protect the league's
OL,11,Fcompetitiveness by ensuring clubs
OL,12,Fcan't take advantage of artificially
OL,13,Finflated deals with companies linked
OL,14,Fto their owners. As things stand, all
OL,15,Fcontracts must represent "fair market
OL,16,Fvalue."
OL,18,FAt a private arbitration hearing in
OL,19,FJune, City's lawyers argued the
OL,20,Fcurrent regulations were anti-
OL,21,Fcompetitive.
