OL,7,FUnder the APT restrictions, one of the
OL,8,Ftools used by the League to assess
OL,9,Fwhether a contract is reasonable or
OL,10,Fnot, is a databank where clubs are
OL,11,Frequired to register the size of their
OL,12,Fcommercial deals.
OL,14,FThe Premier League was hoping to
OL,15,Fintroduce an amendment to that clause
OL,16,Ftoday, but at the last minute pulled
OL,17,Fit from a vote.
