OL,7,FSome sources suggest that to interpret
OL,8,Fthat as a victory for Manchester City
OL,9,Fand its case against the Premier
OL,10,FLeague over APT is misguided.
OL,12,FOthers though, close to the process,
OL,13,Ftake a different view and believe it
OL,14,Fto be a very significant moment, not
OL,15,Fjust in City's fight against APT but
OL,16,Fthe 100 plus charges they face in a
OL,17,Fseparate case brought by the Premier
OL,18,FLeague.
