OL,7,FThat hearing, again in private, is now
OL,8,Finto its second week and a judgement
OL,9,Fis not expected until sometime next
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FBefore then, if City were successful
OL,13,Fin their APT challenge, the current
OL,14,Farrangements would need to be
OL,15,Fsignificantly altered and all 20
OL,16,FPremier League clubs would have to
OL,17,Fvote on those changes.
