OL,7,FWhen asked about the prospect of that,
OL,8,Fone senior executive who was at
OL,9,Ftoday's meeting told ITV News "I don't
OL,10,Fexpect it to happen."
OL,12,FClub executives did get an update on
OL,13,Fthe Premier League's legal bills which
OL,14,Fare racking up in unprecedented
OL,15,Ffashion. In addition to the two cases
OL,16,Fagainst Manchester City, it has dealt
OL,17,Fwith financial fair play breaches by
OL,18,FEverton, Nottingham Forest and
OL,19,FLeicester City, as well as conducting
OL,20,Fvarious other investigations including
OL,21,Finto Chelsea.
